33//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
34extern const char* Mpegv_colour_primaries(int8u colour_primaries)
35{
36 switch (colour_primaries)
37 {
38 case 1 : return "BT.709";
39 case 4 : return "BT.470 System M";
40 case 5 : return "BT.601 PAL";
41 case 6 : return "BT.601 NTSC";
42 case 7 : return "SMPTE 240M"; //Same as BT.601 NTSC
43 case 8 : return "Generic film";
44 case 9 : return "BT.2020"; //Added in HEVC
45 case 10 : return "XYZ"; //Added in HEVC 2014
46 case 11 : return "SMPTE RP 431-2"; //Added in ISO 23001-8:201x/PDAM1
47 case 12 : return "SMPTE EG 432-1"; //Added in ISO 23001-8:201x/PDAM1
48 case 22 : return "EBU Tech 3213"; //Added in ISO 23001-8:201x/PDAM1
49 default : return "";
50 }
51}
52
53//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
54extern const char* Mpegv_transfer_characteristics(int8u transfer_characteristics)
55{
56 switch (transfer_characteristics)
57 {
58 case 1 : return "BT.709"; //Same as BT.609
59 case 4 : return "BT.470 System M";
60 case 5 : return "BT.470 System B, BT.470 System G";
61 case 6 : return "BT.601";
62 case 7 : return "SMPTE 240M";
63 case 8 : return "Linear";
64 case 9 : return "Logarithmic (100:1)"; //Added in MPEG-4 Visual
65 case 10 : return "Logarithmic (316.22777:1)"; //Added in MPEG-4 Visual
66 case 11 : return "IEC 61966-2-4"; //Added in AVC
67 case 12 : return "BT.1361 extended colour gamut system"; //Added in AVC
68 case 13 : return "sYCC"; //Added in HEVC
69 case 14 : return "BT.2020"; //Added in HEVC
70 case 15 : return "BT.2020"; //Added in HEVC
71 case 16 : return "SMPTE ST 2084"; //Added in HEVC 2015
72 case 17 : return "SMPTE ST 428-1"; //Added in HEVC 2015
73 case 18 : return "HLG"; //Added in ISO 23001-8:201x/PDAM1
74 default : return "";
75 }
76}
77
78//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
79extern const char* Mpegv_matrix_coefficients(int8u matrix_coefficients)
80{
81 switch (matrix_coefficients)
82 {
83 case 0 : return "RGB"; //Added in AVC
84 case 1 : return "BT.709";
85 case 4 : return "FCC 73.682";
86 case 5 : return "BT.601";
87 case 6 : return "BT.601";
88 case 7 : return "SMPTE 240M";
89 case 8 : return "YCgCo"; //Added in AVC
90 case 9 : return "BT.2020 non-constant"; //Added in HEVC
91 case 10 : return "BT.2020 constant"; //Added in HEVC
92 case 11 : return "Chroma-derived non-constant"; //Added in ISO 23001-8:201x/PDAM1
93 case 12 : return "Chroma-derived constant"; //Added in ISO 23001-8:201x/PDAM1
94 default : return "";
95 }
96}

98} //NameSpace

148//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
149const char* Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication (int8u profile_and_level_indication)
150{
151 switch (profile_and_level_indication)
152 {
153 case 0x82 : return "4:2:2@High";
154 case 0x85 : return "4:2:2@Main";
155 case 0x8A : return "Multi-view@High";
156 case 0x8B : return "Multi-view@High-1440";
157 case 0x8D : return "Multi-view@Main";
158 case 0x8E : return "Multi-view@Low";
159 default : return "";
160 }
161};

1166
1167//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1168void File_Mpegv::Streams_Update()
1169{
1170 for (size_t Text_Positions_Pos=0; Text_Positions_Pos<Text_Positions.size(); Text_Positions_Pos++)
1171 {
1172 if (*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser && (*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)->Status[IsUpdated])
1173 {
1174 Update(*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser);
1175 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<(*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)->Count_Get(Stream_Text); Pos++)
1176 {
1177 //Saving previous Muxing mode
1178 Ztring MuxingMode=Retrieve(Stream_Text, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos, "MuxingMode");
1179
1180 bool IsNewStream=false;
1181 if (Retrieve(Stream_Text, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos, Text_ID)!=(*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)->Get(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_ID))
1182 {
1183 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Text, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos);
1184 for (size_t Text_Positions_Pos2=Text_Positions_Pos+1; Text_Positions_Pos2<Text_Positions.size(); Text_Positions_Pos2++)
1185 Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos2].StreamPos++;
1186 IsNewStream=true;
1187 }
1188 Merge(*(*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser), Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos);
1189 Ztring LawRating=(*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating);
1190 if (!LawRating.empty())
1191 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating, LawRating, true);
1192 Ztring Title=(*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title);
1193 if (!Title.empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title).empty())
1194 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Title, Title);
1195
1196 if (IsNewStream)
1197 {
1198 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1199 if ((*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)==GA94_03_Parser)
1200 MuxingMode=__T("A/53 / ")+Retrieve(Stream_Text, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos, "MuxingMode");
1201 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1202 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES)
1203 if ((*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)==Scte_Parser)
1204 MuxingMode=Retrieve(Stream_Text, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos, "MuxingMode");
1205 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1206 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_GXF_YES) && defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
1207 if ((*Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].Parser)==Cdp_Parser)
1208 MuxingMode=__T("Ancillary data / ")+Retrieve(Stream_Text, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos, "MuxingMode");
1209 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_GXF_YES) && defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
1210 }
1211 Fill(Stream_Text, Text_Positions[Text_Positions_Pos].StreamPos+Pos, "MuxingMode", MuxingMode, true);
1212 }
1213 }
1214 }
1215}
1216
1217//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1218void File_Mpegv::Streams_Fill()
1219{
1220 //Version
1221 if (MPEG_Version==2)
1222 {
1223 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format_Version, "Version 2");
1224 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format, "MPEG Video");
1225 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Version, "Version 2");
1226 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Commercial, "MPEG-2 Video");
1227 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec, "MPEG-2V");
1228 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_String, "MPEG-2 Video", Unlimited, true, true);
1229 }
1230 else
1231 {
1232 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format_Version, "Version 1");
1233 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format, "MPEG Video");
1234 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Version, "Version 1");
1235 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Commercial, "MPEG-1 Video");
1236 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec, "MPEG-1V");
1237 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_String, "MPEG-1 Video", Unlimited, true, true);
1238 }
1239
1240 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Width, 0x1000*horizontal_size_extension+horizontal_size_value);
1241 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Height, 0x1000*vertical_size_extension+vertical_size_value);
1242 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Colorimetry, Mpegv_Colorimetry_format[chroma_format]);
1243 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ColorSpace, "YUV");
1244 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitDepth, 8);
1245
1246 //AspectRatio
1247 if (MPEG_Version==2)
1248 {
1249 if (aspect_ratio_information==0)
1250 ;//Forbidden
1251 else if (aspect_ratio_information==1)
1252 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_PixelAspectRatio, 1.000, 3, true);
1253 else if (display_horizontal_size && display_vertical_size)
1254 {
1255 if (vertical_size_value && Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information])
1256 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_DisplayAspectRatio, (float)(0x1000*horizontal_size_extension+horizontal_size_value)/(0x1000*vertical_size_extension+vertical_size_value)
1257 *Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information]/((float)display_horizontal_size/display_vertical_size), 3, true);
1258 }
1259 else if (Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information])
1260 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_DisplayAspectRatio, Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information], 3, true);
1261 }
1262 else //Version 1
1263 {
1264 if (vertical_size_value && Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information])
1265 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_DisplayAspectRatio, (float)(0x1000*horizontal_size_extension+horizontal_size_value)/(0x1000*vertical_size_extension+vertical_size_value)/Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information], 3, true);
1266 }
1267
1268 //FrameRate
1269 if (Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code])
1270 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_FrameRate, Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code] * (frame_rate_extension_n + 1) / (frame_rate_extension_d + 1));
1271
1272 //BitRate
1273 if (vbv_delay==0xFFFF || (MPEG_Version==1 && bit_rate_value==0x3FFFF))
1274 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate_Mode, "VBR");
1275 if (bit_rate_value_IsValid && (bit_rate_extension>0 || bit_rate_value!=0x3FFFF))
1276 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate_Maximum, ((((int32u)bit_rate_extension<<12))+bit_rate_value)*400);
1277
1278 //Interlacement
1279 if (MPEG_Version==1)
1280 {
1281 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Progressive");
1282 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "PPF");
1283 }
1284 else if (progressive_frame_Count && progressive_frame_Count!=Frame_Count && progressive_frame_Count!=Frame_Count+1) //In case the stream is cut before a slice
1285 {
1286 //This is mixed
1287 }
1288 else if (Frame_Count>0) //Only if we have at least one progressive_frame definition
1289 {
1290 if (progressive_sequence || progressive_frame_Count==Frame_Count || progressive_frame_Count==Frame_Count+1)
1291 {
1292 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Progressive");
1293 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "PPF");
1294 if (!progressive_sequence && !(Interlaced_Top && Interlaced_Bottom) && !(!Interlaced_Top && !Interlaced_Bottom))
1295 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, Interlaced_Top?"TFF":"BFF");
1296 }
1297 else
1298 {
1299 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Interlaced");
1300 if ((Interlaced_Top && Interlaced_Bottom) || (!Interlaced_Top && !Interlaced_Bottom))
1301 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "Interlaced");
1302 else
1303 {
1304 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, Interlaced_Top?"TFF":"BFF");
1305 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, Interlaced_Top?"TFF":"BFF");
1306 }
1307 if (!(PictureStructure_Field && PictureStructure_Frame) && !(!PictureStructure_Field && !PictureStructure_Frame))
1308 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_PictureStructure, PictureStructure_Field?"Field":"Frame");
1309 }
1310 std::string TempRef;
1311 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<TemporalReference.size(); Pos++)
1312 if (TemporalReference[Pos] && TemporalReference[Pos]->HasPictureCoding)
1313 {
1314 TempRef+=TemporalReference[Pos]->top_field_first?"T":"B";
1315 TempRef+=TemporalReference[Pos]->repeat_first_field?"3":"2";
1316 }
1317 if (TempRef.find('3')!=std::string::npos)
1318 {
1319 if (TempRef.find("T2T3B2B3T2T3B2B3")!=std::string::npos
1320 || TempRef.find("B2B3T2T3B2B3T2T3")!=std::string::npos)
1321 {
1322 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, "2:3 Pulldown", Unlimited, true, true);
1323 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate, FrameRate*24/30, 3, true); //Real framerate
1324 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Progressive", Unlimited, true, true);
1325 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "PPF", Unlimited, true, true);
1326 }
1327 if (TempRef.find("T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T3B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B3")!=std::string::npos
1328 || TempRef.find("B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B2B3T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T2T3")!=std::string::npos)
1329 {
1330 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, "2:2:2:2:2:2:2:2:2:2:2:3 Pulldown", Unlimited, true, true);
1331 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate, FrameRate*24/25, 3, true); //Real framerate
1332 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Progressive", Unlimited, true, true);
1333 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "PPF", Unlimited, true, true);
1334 }
1335 }
1336 }
1337
1338 //Profile
1339 if (!profile_and_level_indication_escape && profile_and_level_indication_profile!=(int8u)-1 && profile_and_level_indication_level!=(int8u)-1)
1340 {
1341 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile, Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_profile[profile_and_level_indication_profile])+__T("@")+Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_level[profile_and_level_indication_level]));
1342 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Profile, Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_profile[profile_and_level_indication_profile])+__T("@")+Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_level[profile_and_level_indication_level]));
1343 }
1344 else if (profile_and_level_indication_escape)
1345 {
1346 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile, Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication(profile_and_level_indication)));
1347 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Profile, Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication(profile_and_level_indication)));
1348 }
1349
1350 //Standard
1351 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Standard, Mpegv_video_format[video_format]);
1352 if (colour_description)
1353 {
1354 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_colour_description_present, "Yes");
1355 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_colour_primaries, Mpegv_colour_primaries(colour_primaries));
1356 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_transfer_characteristics, Mpegv_transfer_characteristics(transfer_characteristics));
1357 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_matrix_coefficients, Mpegv_matrix_coefficients(matrix_coefficients));
1358 }
1359
1360 //Matrix
1361 if (load_intra_quantiser_matrix || load_non_intra_quantiser_matrix)
1362 {
1363 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings, "CustomMatrix");
1364 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_Matrix, "Custom");
1365 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_Matrix_Data, Matrix_intra);
1366 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_Matrix_Data, Matrix_nonintra);
1367 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings, "CustomMatrix");
1368 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings_Matrix, "Custom");
1369 }
1370 else
1371 {
1372 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_Matrix, "Default");
1373 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings_Matrix, "Default");
1374 }
1375
1376 //library
1377 if (Library.size()>=8)
1378 {
1379 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Encoded_Library, Library);
1380 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Encoded_Library_Name, Library_Name);
1381 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Encoded_Library_Version, Library_Version);
1382 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Encoded_Library, Library);
1383 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Encoded_Library_Name, Library_Name);
1384 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Encoded_Library_Version, Library_Version);
1385 }
1386
1387 //Delay
1388 if (group_start_FirstPass && !TimeCodeIsNotTrustable && Time_Begin_Seconds!=Error)
1389 {
1390 float64 Time_Begin=((float64)Time_Begin_Seconds)*1000;
1391 if (FrameRate)
1392 Time_Begin+=((float64)Time_Begin_Frames)*1000/FrameRate;
1393 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay, Time_Begin, 0);
1394 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay_Settings, Ztring(__T("drop_frame_flag="))+(group_start_drop_frame_flag?__T("1"):__T("0")));
1395 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay_Settings, Ztring(__T("closed_gop="))+(group_start_closed_gop?__T("1"):__T("0")));
1396 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay_Settings, Ztring(__T("broken_link="))+(group_start_broken_link?__T("1"):__T("0")));
1397 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay_Source, "Stream");
1398 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay_DropFrame, group_start_drop_frame_flag?"Yes":"No");
1399
1400 if (group_start_closed_gop_Closed+group_start_closed_gop_Open>=4
1401 && ((group_start_closed_gop && group_start_closed_gop_Closed==1)
1402 || group_start_closed_gop_Closed==0
1403 || group_start_closed_gop_Open==0)) // Testing a couple of GOPs, and coherant
1404 {
1405 if (group_start_closed_gop_Open)
1406 {
1407 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, "Gop_OpenClosed", "Open");
1408 if (group_start_closed_gop)
1409 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, "Gop_OpenClosed_FirstFrame", "Closed");
1410 }
1411 else
1412 {
1413 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, "Gop_OpenClosed", "Closed");
1414 }
1415 }
1416
1417 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_TimeCode_FirstFrame, TimeCode_FirstFrame.c_str());
1418 if (IsSub)
1419 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_TimeCode_Source, "Group of pictures header");
1420 }
1421
1422 //BVOP
1423 if (BVOP_Count>0)
1424 {
1425 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings, "BVOP");
1426 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_BVOP, "Yes");
1427 }
1428 else
1429 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_BVOP, "No");
1430
1431 //Buffer
1432 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BufferSize, 2*1024*((((int32u)vbv_buffer_size_extension)<<10)+vbv_buffer_size_value));
1433
1434 //Autorisation of other streams
1435 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
1436 {
1437 NextCode_Clear();
1438 NextCode_Add(0x00);
1439 NextCode_Add(0xB8);
1440 }
1441 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
1442 if (!Macroblocks_Parse)
1443 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
1444 for (int8u Pos=0x01; Pos<=0xAF; Pos++)
1445 Streams[Pos].Searching_Payload=false;
1446 Streams[0xB8].Searching_TimeStamp_End=true;
1447 if (IsSub)
1448 {
1449 Streams[0xB3].Searching_TimeStamp_End=true;
1450 Streams[0x00].Searching_TimeStamp_End=true;
1451 }
1452
1453 //Caption may be in user_data, must be activated if full parsing is requested
1454 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES) || (defined(MEDIAINFO_GXF_YES) && defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES))
1455 Streams[0x00].Searching_Payload=GA94_03_IsPresent || Cdp_IsPresent;
1456 Streams[0xB2].Searching_Payload=GA94_03_IsPresent || CC___IsPresent || Scte_IsPresent;
1457 Streams[0xB3].Searching_Payload=GA94_03_IsPresent || Cdp_IsPresent;
1458 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES) || (defined(MEDIAINFO_GXF_YES) && defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES))
1459 if (Config->ParseSpeed>=1)
1460 {
1461 Streams[0x00].Searching_Payload=true;
1462 Streams[0xB2].Searching_Payload=true;
1463 Streams[0xB3].Searching_Payload=true;
1464 Streams[0xB5].Searching_Payload=true;
1465 }
1466
1467 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1468 if (DTG1_Parser)
1469 Merge(*DTG1_Parser, Stream_Video, 0, 0);
1470 if (GA94_06_Parser)
1471 {
1472 Merge(*GA94_06_Parser, Stream_Video, 0, 0);
1473 Ztring LawRating=GA94_06_Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating);
1474 if (!LawRating.empty())
1475 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating, LawRating, true);
1476 Ztring Title=GA94_06_Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title);
1477 if (!Title.empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title).empty())
1478 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Title, Title);
1479 }
1480 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1481 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1482 if (AfdBarData_Parser)
1483 Merge(*AfdBarData_Parser, Stream_Video, 0, 0);
1484 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1485
1486 //extra
1487 if (intra_dc_precision!=(int8u)-1)
1488 {
1489 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, "intra_dc_precision", 8+intra_dc_precision);
1490 (*Stream_More)[Stream_Video][0](Ztring().From_Local("intra_dc_precision"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
1491 }
1492
1493 //Commercial name
1494 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Version)==__T("Version 2")
1495 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_DisplayAspectRatio)==__T("1.778")
1496 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitDepth)==__T("8")
1497 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ChromaSubsampling)==__T("4:2:0"))
1498 {
1499 //HDV1
1500 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Width)==__T("1280")
1501 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Height)==__T("720")
1502 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType)==__T("Progressive")
1503 && (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("60.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("59.940") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("30.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("29.970") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("24.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("23.976") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("50.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("25.000"))
1504 && (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile)==__T("Main@High") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile)==__T("Main@High 1440"))
1505 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate).To_int64u()<20000000 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate_Maximum).To_int64u()<20000000)
1506 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny, "HDV 720p");
1507
1508 //HDV2
1509 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Width)==__T("1440")
1510 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Height)==__T("1080")
1511 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile)==__T("Main@High 1440")
1512 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate).To_int64u()<27000000 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate_Maximum).To_int64u()<27000000)
1513 {
1514 //Interlaced
1515 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType)==__T("Interlaced")
1516 && (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("30.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("29.970") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("50.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("25.000")))
1517 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny, "HDV 1080i");
1518
1519 //Progressive
1520 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType)==__T("Progressive")
1521 && (Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("30.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("29.970") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("24.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("23.976") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("50.000") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameRate)==__T("25.000")))
1522 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny, "HDV 1080p");
1523 }
1524 }
1525}
1526
1527//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1528void File_Mpegv::Streams_Finish()
1529{
1530 //Duration
1531 if (PTS_End>PTS_Begin)
1532 {
1533 if (PTS_End_temporal_reference<temporal_reference_Max)
1534 {
1535 int64u tc_ToAdd=tc/((progressive_sequence || picture_structure==3)?1:2); //Progressive of Frame
1536 PTS_End+=tc_ToAdd*(temporal_reference_Max-PTS_End_temporal_reference-1); //TODO: handle cases with 3:2 Pulldown (different progressive_sequence / picture_structure)
1537 }
1538 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Duration, float64_int64s(((float64)(PTS_End-PTS_Begin))/1000000));
1539 }
1540 else if (Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1)
1541 {
1542 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameCount, Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded);
1543 if (FrameRate)
1544 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Duration, Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded/FrameRate*1000, 0);
1545 }
1546 else if (!TimeCodeIsNotTrustable && Time_End_Seconds!=Error && FrameRate)
1547 {
1548 TimeCode Time_Begin_TC;
1549 Time_Begin_TC.FramesPerSecond=(int8u)ceil(FrameRate);
1550 Time_Begin_TC.DropFrame=group_start_IsParsed?group_start_drop_frame_flag:((FrameRate-ceil(FrameRate))?true:false);
1551 Time_Begin_TC.Hours=(int8u)(Time_Begin_Seconds/3600);
1552 Time_Begin_TC.Minutes=(int8u)((Time_Begin_Seconds%3600)/60);
1553 Time_Begin_TC.Seconds=(int8u)(Time_Begin_Seconds%60);
1554 Time_Begin_TC.Frames=(int8u)Time_Begin_Frames;
1555 TimeCode Time_End_TC;
1556 Time_End_TC.FramesPerSecond=(int8u)ceil(FrameRate);
1557 Time_End_TC.DropFrame=Time_Begin_TC.DropFrame;
1558 Time_End_TC.Hours=(int8u)(Time_End_Seconds/3600);
1559 Time_End_TC.Minutes=(int8u)((Time_End_Seconds%3600)/60);
1560 Time_End_TC.Seconds=(int8u)(Time_End_Seconds%60);
1561 Time_End_TC.Frames=(int8u)Time_End_Frames;
1562 int64u Time_Begin_FrameCount=Time_Begin_TC.ToFrames();
1563 int64u Time_End_FrameCount = Time_End_TC.ToFrames();
1564 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_FrameCount, Time_End_FrameCount-Time_Begin_FrameCount, 0);
1565 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Duration, (Time_End_FrameCount-Time_Begin_FrameCount)/FrameRate*1000, 0);
1566 }
1567
1568 //picture_coding_types
1569 if (!picture_coding_types.empty())
1570 {
1571 int64u MaxCount=0;
1572 int64u Total=0;
1573 string MaxCount_type;
1574 for (std::map<std::string, int64u>::iterator Temp=picture_coding_types.begin(); Temp!=picture_coding_types.end(); ++Temp)
1575 {
1576 if (Temp->second>MaxCount)
1577 {
1578 MaxCount=Temp->second;
1579 MaxCount_type=Temp->first;
1580 }
1581 Total+=Temp->second;
1582 }
1583
1584 if (Total>=4)
1585 {
1586 int64u Count=0;
1587 for (std::map<std::string, int64u>::iterator Temp=picture_coding_types.begin(); Temp!=picture_coding_types.end(); ++Temp)
1588 if (Temp->first!=MaxCount_type)
1589 Count+=Temp->second;
1590
1591 if (Count<Total/2 && Count<Config_VariableGopDetection_Occurences)
1592 {
1593 size_t M=1;
1594 size_t M_Max=1;
1595 for (size_t Pos=1; Pos<MaxCount_type.size(); Pos++)
1596 if (MaxCount_type[Pos]==__T('B'))
1597 {
1598 M++;
1599 if (M>M_Max)
1600 M_Max=M;
1601 }
1602 else
1603 M=1;
1604 Ztring GOP;
1605 if (M_Max>1)
1606 {
1607 GOP+=__T("M=");
1608 GOP+=Ztring::ToZtring(M_Max);
1609 GOP+=__T(", ");
1610 }
1611 GOP+=__T("N=");
1612 GOP+=Ztring::ToZtring(MaxCount_type.size());
1613 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_GOP, GOP, true);
1614 }
1615 else
1616 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_GOP, "Variable", Unlimited, true, true);
1617 }
1618 }
1619
1620 //InitDataNotRepeated
1621 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1622 if (!InitDataNotRepeated_Optional && Config_InitDataNotRepeated_Occurences!=(int64u)-1)
1623 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, "InitDataRepeated", InitDataNotRepeated>=Config_InitDataNotRepeated_Occurences?"No":"Yes", Unlimited, true, true);
1624 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1625
1626 //Other parsers
1627 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1628 if (GA94_03_Parser && !GA94_03_Parser->Status[IsFinished] && GA94_03_Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
1629 Finish(GA94_03_Parser);
1630 if (CC___Parser && !CC___Parser->Status[IsFinished] && CC___Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
1631 Finish(CC___Parser);
1632 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1633 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES)
1634 if (Scte_Parser && !Scte_Parser->Status[IsFinished] && Scte_Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
1635 Finish(Scte_Parser);
1636 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES)
1637 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1638 if (DTG1_Parser && !DTG1_Parser->Status[IsFinished] && DTG1_Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
1639 {
1640 Finish(DTG1_Parser);
1641 Merge(*DTG1_Parser, Stream_Video, 0, 0);
1642 }
1643 if (GA94_06_Parser && !GA94_06_Parser->Status[IsFinished] && GA94_06_Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
1644 {
1645 Finish(GA94_06_Parser);
1646 Merge(*GA94_06_Parser, Stream_Video, 0, 0);
1647 }
1648 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1649 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
1650 if (Cdp_Parser && !Cdp_Parser->Status[IsFinished] && Cdp_Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
1651 Finish(Cdp_Parser);
1652 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
1653 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1654 if (AfdBarData_Parser && !AfdBarData_Parser->Status[IsFinished] && AfdBarData_Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
1655 {
1656 Finish(AfdBarData_Parser);
1657 Merge(*AfdBarData_Parser, Stream_Video, 0, 0);
1658 }
1659 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
1660
1661 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1662 int64u Numerator=0, Denominator=0;
1663 switch (frame_rate_code)
1664 {
1665 case 1 : Numerator=24000; Denominator=1001; break;
1666 case 2 : Numerator=24; Denominator=1; break;
1667 case 3 : Numerator=25; Denominator=1; break;
1668 case 4 : Numerator=30000; Denominator=1001; break;
1669 case 5 : Numerator=30; Denominator=1; break;
1670 case 6 : Numerator=50; Denominator=1; break;
1671 case 7 : Numerator=60000; Denominator=1001; break;
1672 case 8 : Numerator=60; Denominator=1; break;
1673 default: ;
1674 }
1675 if (Numerator)
1676 {
1677 Numerator*=frame_rate_extension_n+1;
1678 Denominator*=frame_rate_extension_d+1;
1679 Ibi_Stream_Finish(Numerator, Denominator);
1680 }
1681 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1682}

1684//***************************************************************************
1685// Buffer - Synchro
1686//***************************************************************************
1687
1688//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1689bool File_Mpegv::Synched_Test()
1690{
1691 //Must have enough buffer for having header
1692 if (Buffer_Offset+4>Buffer_Size)
1693 return false;
1694
1695 //Quick test of synchro
1696 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
1697 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00
1698 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x01)
1699 {
1700 Synched=false;
1701 return true;
1702 }
1703
1704 //Quick search
1705 if (!Header_Parser_QuickSearch())
1706 return false;
1707
1708 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1709 if ((Ibi_SliceParsed && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]==0x00)) || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]==0xB3) // picture_start without sequence_header or sequence_header
1710 {
1711 if (Buffer_Offset+6>Buffer_Size)
1712 return false;
1713 bool RandomAccess=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+5]&0x38)==0x08 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]==0xB3; //picture_start with I-Frame || sequence_header
1714 if (RandomAccess)
1715 Ibi_Add();
1716
1717 Ibi_SliceParsed=false;
1718 }
1719 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1720
1721 //We continue
1722 return true;
1723}

1858//***************************************************************************
1859// Buffer - Demux
1860//***************************************************************************
1861
1862//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1863#if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1864bool File_Mpegv::Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Test()
1865{
1866 if ((Demux_IntermediateItemFound && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]==0x00) || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]==0xB3)
1867 {
1868 if (Demux_Offset==0)
1869 {
1870 Demux_Offset=Buffer_Offset;
1871 Demux_IntermediateItemFound=false;
1872 }
1873 if (IsSub && ParserIDs[0]==MediaInfo_Parser_Mxf) //TODO: find a better way to demux, currently implemeted this way because we need I-frame status info from MXF
1874 {
1875 Demux_Offset=Buffer_Size;
1876 Demux_IntermediateItemFound=true;
1877 }
1878 else
1879 {
1880 while (Demux_Offset+4<=Buffer_Size)
1881 {
1882 //Synchronizing
1883 while(Demux_Offset+4<=Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Demux_Offset ]!=0x00
1884 || Buffer[Demux_Offset+1]!=0x00
1885 || Buffer[Demux_Offset+2]!=0x01))
1886 {
1887 Demux_Offset+=2;
1888 while(Demux_Offset<Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset]!=0x00)
1889 Demux_Offset+=2;
1890 if (Demux_Offset>=Buffer_Size || Buffer[Demux_Offset-1]==0x00)
1891 Demux_Offset--;
1892 }
1893 if (Demux_Offset+4>Buffer_Size)
1894 {
1895 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Size==File_Size)
1896 Demux_Offset=Buffer_Size;
1897 break;
1898 }
1899
1900 if (Demux_IntermediateItemFound)
1901 {
1902 bool MustBreak;
1903 switch (Buffer[Demux_Offset+3])
1904 {
1905 case 0x00 :
1906 case 0xB3 :
1907 MustBreak=true; break;
1908 default :
1909 Demux_Offset+=3;
1910 MustBreak=false;
1911 }
1912 if (MustBreak)
1913 break; //while() loop
1914 }
1915 else
1916 {
1917 if (!Buffer[Demux_Offset+3])
1918 Demux_IntermediateItemFound=true;
1919 }
1920
1921 Demux_Offset++;
1922 }
1923
1924 if (Demux_Offset+4>Buffer_Size && File_Offset+Buffer_Size!=File_Size)
1925 return false; //No complete frame
1926 }
1927
1928 bool RandomAccess=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]==0xB3;
1929 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
1930 {
1931 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1932 return false;
1933 File_Mpegv* MI=new File_Mpegv;
1934 Element_Code=(int64u)-1;
1935 Open_Buffer_Init(MI);
1936 Open_Buffer_Continue(MI, Buffer, Buffer_Size);
1937 bool IsOk=MI->Status[IsAccepted];
1938 delete MI;
1939 if (!IsOk)
1940 return false;
1941 }
1942 if (IFrame_IsParsed || RandomAccess)
1943 Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Demux(RandomAccess);
1944 else
1945 Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Demux_Clear();
1946 }
1947
1948 return true;
1949}
1950#endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX

1954//***************************************************************************

1956//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1957void File_Mpegv::Read_Buffer_Unsynched()
1958{
1959 for (int8u Pos=0x00; Pos<0xB9; Pos++)
1960 {
1961 Streams[Pos].Searching_Payload=false;
1962 Streams[Pos].Searching_TimeStamp_Start=false;
1963 Streams[Pos].Searching_TimeStamp_End=false;
1964 }
1965 Streams[0xB3].Searching_TimeStamp_End=true; //sequence_header
1966 Streams[0xB8].Searching_TimeStamp_End=true; //group_start
1967 Time_End_Seconds=Error;
1968 Time_End_Frames=(int8u)-1;
1969 RefFramesCount=0;
1970 sequence_header_IsParsed=false;
1971 group_start_IsParsed=false;
1972 PTS_LastIFrame=(int64u)-1;
1973 IFrame_IsParsed=false;
1974 picture_coding_types_Current.clear();
1975 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1976 Ibi_SliceParsed=true;
1977 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1978 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
1979 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
1980 {
1981 macroblock_x_PerFrame=0;
1982 macroblock_y_PerFrame=0;
1983 }
1984 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
1985
1986 temporal_reference_Old=(int16u)-1;
1987 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<TemporalReference.size(); Pos++)
1988 delete TemporalReference[Pos]; //TemporalReference[Pos]=NULL;
1989 TemporalReference.clear();
1990 TemporalReference_Offset=0;
1991 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1992 GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset=0;
1993 if (GA94_03_Parser)
1994 GA94_03_Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1995 if (CC___Parser)
1996 CC___Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1997 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1998 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES)
1999 Scte_TemporalReference_Offset=0;
2000 if (Scte_Parser)
2001 Scte_Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
2002 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES)
2003 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
2004 if (DTG1_Parser)
2005 DTG1_Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
2006 if (GA94_06_Parser)
2007 GA94_06_Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
2008 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
2009 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
2010 if (Cdp_Parser)
2011 Cdp_Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
2012 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
2013 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
2014 if (AfdBarData_Parser)
2015 AfdBarData_Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
2016 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
2017
2018 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_ANCILLARY_YES)
2019 if (Ancillary && *Ancillary && (*Ancillary)->Cdp_Data.empty())
2020 (*Ancillary)->AspectRatio=0;
2021 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_ANCILLARY_YES)
2022
2023 //NextCode
2024 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
2025 {
2026 NextCode_Clear();
2027 NextCode_Add(0xB3);
2028 NextCode_Add(0xB8);
2029 }
2030}

2032//***************************************************************************
2033// Buffer - Per element
2034//***************************************************************************
2035
2036//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2037void File_Mpegv::Header_Parse()
2038{
2039 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2040 if (Trace_Activated)
2041 {
2042 //Parsing
2043 int8u start_code;
2044 Skip_B3( "synchro");
2045 Get_B1 (start_code, "start_code");
2046 if (!Header_Parser_Fill_Size())
2047 {
2048 Element_WaitForMoreData();
2049 return;
2050 }
2051
2052 //Filling
2053 Header_Fill_Code(start_code, Ztring().From_CC1(start_code));
2054 }
2055 else
2056 {
2057 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2058 //Parsing
2059 int8u start_code=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3];
2060 Element_Offset+=4;
2061 if (!Header_Parser_Fill_Size())
2062 {
2063 Element_WaitForMoreData();
2064 return;
2065 }
2066
2067 //Filling
2068 Header_Fill_Code(start_code, Ztring().From_CC1(start_code));
2069 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2070 }
2071 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2072}
2073
2074//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2075bool File_Mpegv::Header_Parser_Fill_Size()
2076{
2077 //Look for next Sync word
2078 if (Buffer_Offset_Temp==0) //Buffer_Offset_Temp is not 0 if Header_Parse_Fill_Size() has already parsed first frames
2079 Buffer_Offset_Temp=Buffer_Offset+4;
2080 while (Buffer_Offset_Temp+4<=Buffer_Size
2081 && CC3(Buffer+Buffer_Offset_Temp)!=0x000001)
2082 {
2083 Buffer_Offset_Temp+=2;
2084 while(Buffer_Offset_Temp<Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Temp]!=0x00)
2085 Buffer_Offset_Temp+=2;
2086 if (Buffer_Offset_Temp>=Buffer_Size || Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Temp-1]==0x00)
2087 Buffer_Offset_Temp--;
2088 }
2089
2090 //Must wait more data?
2091 if (Buffer_Offset_Temp+4>Buffer_Size)
2092 {
2093 if (FrameIsAlwaysComplete || File_Offset+Buffer_Size==File_Size)
2094 Buffer_Offset_Temp=Buffer_Size; //We are sure that the next bytes are a start
2095 else
2096 return false;
2097 }
2098
2099 //OK, we continue
2100 Header_Fill_Size(Buffer_Offset_Temp-Buffer_Offset);
2101 Buffer_Offset_Temp=0;
2102 return true;
2103}
2104
2105//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2106bool File_Mpegv::Header_Parser_QuickSearch()
2107{
2108 while ( Buffer_Offset+4<=Buffer_Size
2109 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]==0x00
2110 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]==0x00
2111 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x01)
2112 {
2113 //Getting start_code
2114 int8u start_code=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3];
2115
2116 //Searching start or timestamp
2117 if (Streams[start_code].Searching_Payload
2118 || Streams[start_code].Searching_TimeStamp_Start
2119 || Streams[start_code].Searching_TimeStamp_End)
2120 return true;
2121
2122 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2123 if (start_code==0xB3) // sequence_header
2124 {
2125 //
2126 Has_sequence_header=true;
2127 }
2128 if (start_code==0xB5) // extension_start
2129 {
2130 if (Buffer_Offset+5>Buffer_Size)
2131 return false;
2132
2133 if ((Buffer[Buffer_Offset+4]&0xF0)==0x10) // sequence_extension
2134 Has_sequence_extension=true;
2135 }
2136 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2137
2138 //Synchronizing
2139 Buffer_Offset+=4;
2140 Synched=false;
2141 if (!Synchronize())
2142 {
2143 UnSynched_IsNotJunk=true;
2144 return false;
2145 }
2146
2147 if (Buffer_Offset+4>Buffer_Size)
2148 {
2149 UnSynched_IsNotJunk=true;
2150 return false;
2151 }
2152 }
2153
2154 Trusted_IsNot("MPEG Video, Synchronisation lost");
2155 return Synchronize();
2156}
2157
2158//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2159void File_Mpegv::Data_Parse()
2160{
2161 //Parsing
2162 switch (Element_Code)
2163 {
2164 case 0x00: picture_start(); break;
2165 case 0xB0: Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Unknown"); break;
2166 case 0xB1: Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Unknown"); break;
2167 case 0xB2: user_data_start(); break;
2168 case 0xB3: sequence_header(); break;
2169 case 0xB4: sequence_error(); break;
2170 case 0xB5: extension_start(); break;
2171 case 0xB6: Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Unknown"); break;
2172 case 0xB7: sequence_end(); break;
2173 case 0xB8: group_start(); break;
2174 default:
2175 if (Element_Code>=0x01
2176 && Element_Code<=0xAF) slice_start();
2177 else
2178 Trusted_IsNot("Unattended element");
2179 }
2180}
2181
2182//***************************************************************************
2183// EOF
2184//***************************************************************************
2185
2186//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2187void File_Mpegv::Detect_EOF()
2188{
2189 if ((IsSub && Status[IsFilled])
2190 || (!IsSub && File_Size>SizeToAnalyse_Begin+SizeToAnalyse_End && File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>SizeToAnalyse_Begin && File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset<File_Size-SizeToAnalyse_End && Config->ParseSpeed<=0.5))
2191 {
2192 if (MustExtendParsingDuration && Frame_Count<Frame_Count_Valid
2193 && !(!IsSub && File_Size>SizeToAnalyse_Begin*10+SizeToAnalyse_End*10 && File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset>SizeToAnalyse_Begin*10 && File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset<File_Size-SizeToAnalyse_End*10))
2194 {
2195 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES) || (defined(MEDIAINFO_GXF_YES) && defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES))
2196 Streams[0x00].Searching_Payload=GA94_03_IsPresent || Cdp_IsPresent;
2197 Streams[0xB2].Searching_Payload=GA94_03_IsPresent || CC___IsPresent || Scte_IsPresent;
2198 Streams[0xB3].Searching_Payload=GA94_03_IsPresent || Cdp_IsPresent;
2199 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES) || (defined(MEDIAINFO_GXF_YES) && defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES))
2200 return;
2201 }
2202
2203 //
2204 Time_End_Seconds=Error;
2205 Time_End_Frames=(int8u)-1;
2206
2207 //Autorisation of other streams
2208 if (!IsSub)
2209 Streams[0x00].Searching_TimeStamp_End=false;
2210
2211 //Jumping
2212 if (!Status[IsFilled])
2213 Fill("MPEG Video");
2214
2215 if (!IsSub)
2216 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
2217 GoToFromEnd(SizeToAnalyse_End, "MPEG Video");
2218 EOF_AlreadyDetected=true; //Sometimes called from Filling
2219 }
2220}
2221
2222//***************************************************************************
2223// Elements
2224//***************************************************************************
2225
2226//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2227// Packet "00"
2228void File_Mpegv::picture_start()
2229{
2230 Element_Name("picture_start");
2231
2232 //Coherency
2233 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
2234 {
2235 if (!NextCode_Test())
2236 return;
2237 }
2238
2239 //Parsing
2240 int8u picture_coding_type_Old=picture_coding_type;
2241 BS_Begin();
2242 Get_S2 (10, temporal_reference, "temporal_reference");
2243 Get_S1 ( 3, picture_coding_type, "picture_coding_type"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_picture_coding_type[picture_coding_type]);
2244 Get_S2 (16, vbv_delay, "vbv_delay");
2245 if (picture_coding_type==2 || picture_coding_type==3) //P or B
2246 {
2247 Skip_S1(1, "full_pel_forward_vector");
2248 Skip_S1(3, "forward_f_code");
2249 }
2250 if (picture_coding_type==3) //B
2251 {
2252 Skip_S1(1, "full_pel_backward_vector");
2253 Skip_S1(3, "backward_f_code");
2254 }
2255 bool extra_bit_picture;
2256 do
2257 {
2258 Peek_SB(extra_bit_picture);
2259 if (extra_bit_picture)
2260 {
2261 Skip_S1(1, "extra_bit_picture");
2262 Skip_S1(8, "extra_information_picture");
2263 }
2264 }
2265 while (extra_bit_picture);
2266 BS_End();
2267
2268 FILLING_BEGIN();
2269 if (picture_coding_type==1)
2270 Frame_Count_LastIFrame=Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded;
2271
2272 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2273 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
2274 {
2275 macroblock_x_PerFrame=0;
2276 macroblock_y_PerFrame=0;
2277 }
2278 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2279
2280 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2281 Slices_Count=0;
2282 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2283 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2284 {
2285 EVENT_BEGIN (Video, SliceInfo, 0)
2286 Event.FieldPosition=Field_Count;
2287 Event.SlicePosition=0;
2288 switch (picture_coding_type)
2289 {
2290 case 1 :
2291 Event.SliceType=0; break;
2292 case 2 :
2293 Event.SliceType=1; break;
2294 case 3 :
2295 Event.SliceType=2; break;
2296 default:
2297 Event.SliceType=(int8u)-1;
2298 }
2299 Event.Flags=0;
2300 EVENT_END ()
2301 }
2302 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2303
2304 //Detection of first I-Frame
2305 if (!IFrame_IsParsed)
2306 {
2307 if (picture_coding_type==1 || picture_coding_type==4) //I-Frame or D-Frame
2308 IFrame_IsParsed=true;
2309 }
2310
2311 if (Frame_Count_LastIFrame!=(int64u)-1)
2312 FrameNumber_PresentationOrder=Frame_Count_LastIFrame+temporal_reference;
2313
2314 //Config
2315 progressive_frame=true;
2316 picture_structure=3; //Frame is default
2317 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2318 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
2319 {
2320 spatial_temporal_weight_code_table_index=0;
2321 f_code[0][0]=0;
2322 f_code[0][1]=0;
2323 f_code[1][0]=0;
2324 f_code[1][1]=0;
2325 sequence_scalable_extension_Present=false;
2326 frame_pred_frame_dct=false;
2327 concealment_motion_vectors=false;
2328 intra_vlc_format=false;
2329 }
2330 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2331
2332 //Temporal reference
2333 if (TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference>=TemporalReference.size())
2334 TemporalReference.resize(TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference+1);
2335 if (TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]==NULL)
2336 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]=new temporalreference;
2337 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->IsValid=true;
2338
2339 //picture_coding_types
2340 if (picture_coding_type==1) //I-Frame
2341 {
2342 if (!picture_coding_types_Current.empty())
2343 {
2344 picture_coding_types[picture_coding_types_Current]++;
2345
2346 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
2347 // Testing if we must give up
2348 if (Config_VariableGopDetection_GiveUp && picture_coding_types.size()>1)
2349 {
2350 int64u MaxCount=0;
2351 string MaxCount_type;
2352 for (std::map<std::string, int64u>::iterator Temp=picture_coding_types.begin(); Temp!=picture_coding_types.end(); ++Temp)
2353 if (Temp->second>MaxCount)
2354 {
2355 MaxCount=Temp->second;
2356 MaxCount_type=Temp->first;
2357 }
2358 int64u Count=0;
2359 for (std::map<std::string, int64u>::iterator Temp=picture_coding_types.begin(); Temp!=picture_coding_types.end(); ++Temp)
2360 if (Temp->first!=MaxCount_type)
2361 Count+=Temp->second;
2362 if (Count>=Config_VariableGopDetection_Occurences)
2363 Config->ParseSpeed=0; // Give up
2364 }
2365 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
2366 }
2367 picture_coding_types_Current='I';
2368 }
2369 else if (!picture_coding_types_Current.empty()) //If an I-Frame is already found
2370 picture_coding_types_Current+=Mpegv_picture_coding_type[picture_coding_type];
2371
2372 //Detecting streams with only I-Frames
2373 if (picture_coding_type==1 && picture_coding_type_Old==1 && !FirstFieldFound)
2374 temporal_reference_Old=(int16u)-1; //Resetting temporal_reference_Old
2375
2376 //NextCode
2377 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
2378 {
2379 NextCode_Clear();
2380 for (int64u Element_Name_Next=0x01; Element_Name_Next<=0xAF; Element_Name_Next++)
2381 NextCode_Add(Element_Name_Next);
2382 NextCode_Add(0xB2);
2383 NextCode_Add(0xB5);
2384 NextCode_Add(0xB8);
2385 }
2386
2387 //Autorisation of other streams
2388 for (int8u Pos=0x01; Pos<=0xAF; Pos++)
2389 Streams[Pos].Searching_Payload=true;
2390 FILLING_END();
2391}
2392
2393//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2394// Packet "01" --> "AF"
2395void File_Mpegv::slice_start()
2396{
2397 //Encryption management
2398 if (CA_system_ID_MustSkipSlices)
2399 {
2400 //Is not decodable
2401 Finish("MPEG Video");
2402 return;
2403 }
2404
2405 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
2406 {
2407 if (!NextCode_Test())
2408 return;
2409 }
2410 Element_Name("slice_start");
2411
2412 //Parsing
2413 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2414 if (Macroblocks_Parse && MPEG_Version==2)
2415 {
2416 BS_Begin();
2417
2418 bool intra_slice_flag;
2419 if (0x1000*vertical_size_extension+vertical_size_value>2800) //vertical_size
2420 Skip_S1(3, "slice_vertical_position_extension");
2421 if (sequence_scalable_extension_Present)
2422 Skip_S1(7, "priority_breakpoint");
2423 Skip_S1(5, "quantiser_scale_code");
2424 Peek_SB(intra_slice_flag);
2425 if (intra_slice_flag)
2426 {
2427 Skip_SB( "intra_slice_flag");
2428 Skip_SB( "intra_slice");
2429 Skip_S1(7, "reserved_bits");
2430 for (;;)
2431 {
2432 bool extra_bit_slice;
2433 Peek_SB(extra_bit_slice);
2434 if (extra_bit_slice)
2435 {
2436 Skip_S1(8, "extra_information_slice");
2437 }
2438 else
2439 break;
2440 if (!Data_BS_Remain())
2441 {
2442 Trusted_IsNot("extra_bit_slice is missing");
2443 return;
2444 }
2445 }
2446 }
2447 Skip_SB( "extra_bit_slice (must be 0)");
2448
2449 macroblock_x=(int64u)-1;
2450 while (Synched) //Synched: testing if this is still valid
2451 {
2452 int8u Remain;
2453 if (Data_BS_Remain()%8)
2454 Peek_S1(Data_BS_Remain()%8, Remain);
2455 else if (Data_Remain())
2456 Remain=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)(Element_Size-Data_Remain())];
2457 else
2458 Remain=0;
2459 if (Remain==0)
2460 {
2461 int32u Remain3;
2462 size_t Bits=Data_BS_Remain();
2463 if (Bits>23)
2464 Bits=23;
2465 Peek_S3((int8u)Bits, Remain3);
2466 if (Remain3==0)
2467 break;
2468 }
2469 slice_start_macroblock();
2470 }
2471
2472 if (Data_BS_Remain())
2473 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "padding");
2474 BS_End();
2475 }
2476 else
2477 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCK
2478 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "data");
2479
2480 FILLING_BEGIN();
2481 int64u tc_ToAdd=tc/((progressive_sequence || picture_structure==3)?1:2); //Progressive of Frame
2482
2483 //Timestamp
2484 if (!TimeCodeIsNotTrustable && group_start_FirstPass && (Time_Begin_Seconds==Error || (Frame_Count<16 && Time_Current_Seconds*FrameRate+Time_Current_Frames+temporal_reference<Time_Begin_Seconds*FrameRate+Time_Begin_Frames))) //Accepting a lower time code at the beginning of the stream
2485 {
2486 Time_Begin_Seconds=Time_Current_Seconds;
2487 Time_Begin_Frames =Time_Current_Frames+(int8u)temporal_reference;
2488 }
2489 if (!TimeCodeIsNotTrustable && (Time_Current_Seconds<Time_Begin_Seconds || (Time_Current_Seconds==Time_Begin_Seconds && Time_Current_Frames+(int8u)temporal_reference<Time_Begin_Frames)))
2490 {
2491 //Time code loop
2492 TimeCodeIsNotTrustable=true;
2493 Time_End_Seconds=(size_t)-1;
2494 }
2495 if (!TimeCodeIsNotTrustable && (picture_coding_type==1 || picture_coding_type==2)) //IFrame or PFrame
2496 {
2497 Time_End_Seconds=Time_Current_Seconds;
2498 Time_End_Frames =Time_Current_Frames+(int8u)temporal_reference;
2499 }
2500
2501 if (temporal_reference==temporal_reference_Old)
2502 {
2503 Frame_Count--;
2504 if (IFrame_IsParsed && Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1)
2505 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded--;
2506 Frame_Count_InThisBlock--;
2507 if (FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
2508 FrameInfo.DTS-=tc_ToAdd;
2509 if (FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1)
2510 FrameInfo.PTS-=tc_ToAdd;
2511 }
2512 else
2513 {
2514 temporal_reference_Old=temporal_reference;
2515 if (temporal_reference_Max<temporal_reference)
2516 temporal_reference_Max=temporal_reference;
2517 }
2518
2519 if (picture_coding_type==1) //IFrame
2520 {
2521 temporal_reference_LastIFrame=temporal_reference;
2522 PTS_LastIFrame=FrameInfo.PTS;
2523 IFrame_Count++;
2524 }
2525 if (PTS_LastIFrame!=(int64u)-1)
2526 {
2527 FrameInfo.PTS=PTS_LastIFrame+(temporal_reference-temporal_reference_LastIFrame)*tc;
2528 if ((PTS_Begin==(int64u)-1 && picture_coding_type==1) //IFrame
2529 || (IFrame_Count<2 && group_start_IsParsed && group_start_closed_gop && FrameInfo.PTS<PTS_Begin))
2530 PTS_Begin=FrameInfo.PTS;
2531 }
2532
2533 //Info
2534 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2535 if (Trace_Activated)
2536 {
2537 Element_Info1(__T("Frame (decoding order) ")+Ztring::ToZtring(Frame_Count));
2538 if (Frame_Count_LastIFrame!=(int64u)-1)
2539 Element_Info1(__T("Frame (presentation order) ")+Ztring::ToZtring(Frame_Count_LastIFrame+temporal_reference));
2540 Element_Info1(__T("picture_coding_type ")+Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_picture_coding_type[picture_coding_type]));
2541 Element_Info1(__T("temporal_reference ")+Ztring::ToZtring(temporal_reference));
2542 if (FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1)
2543 Element_Info1(__T("PTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.PTS)/1000000)));
2544 if (FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
2545 Element_Info1(__T("DTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.DTS)/1000000)));
2546 if (Time_End_Seconds!=Error)
2547 {
2548 int64u Time_End =Time_End_Seconds *1000;
2549 if (FrameRate)
2550 Time_End +=float32_int32s((Time_Current_Frames+temporal_reference)*1000/FrameRate);
2551 size_t Hours =(size_t) Time_End/60/60/1000;
2552 size_t Minutes=(size_t)(Time_End-(Hours*60*60*1000))/60/1000;
2553 size_t Seconds=(size_t)(Time_End-(Hours*60*60*1000)-(Minutes*60*1000))/1000;
2554 size_t Milli =(size_t)(Time_End-(Hours*60*60*1000)-(Minutes*60*1000)-(Seconds*1000));
2555
2556 Ztring Time;
2557 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Hours);
2558 Time+=__T(':');
2559 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Minutes);
2560 Time+=__T(':');
2561 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Seconds);
2562 if (FrameRate!=0)
2563 {
2564 Time+=__T('.');
2565 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Milli);
2566 }
2567 Element_Info1(__T("time_code ")+Time);
2568 }
2569 }
2570 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2571
2572 //CDP
2573 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
2574 if (Ancillary)
2575 {
2576 Cdp_IsPresent=true;
2577 MustExtendParsingDuration=true;
2578 Buffer_TotalBytes_Fill_Max=(int64u)-1; //Disabling this feature for this format, this is done in the parser
2579
2580 Element_Trace_Begin1("CDP");
2581 if ((*Ancillary)==NULL)
2582 (*Ancillary)=new File_Ancillary();
2583 (*Ancillary)->AspectRatio=MPEG_Version==1?Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information]:Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information];
2584 (*Ancillary)->FrameRate=FrameRate;
2585 if ((*Ancillary)->PTS_DTS_Needed)
2586 (*Ancillary)->FrameInfo.DTS=FrameInfo.DTS;
2587 if ((*Ancillary)->Status[IsAccepted]) //In order to test if there is a parser using ancillary data
2588 Open_Buffer_Continue((*Ancillary), Buffer+Buffer_Offset, 0);
2589 Element_Trace_End0();
2590 }
2591 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_CDP_YES)
2592
2593 //Active Format Description & Bar Data
2594 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
2595 if (Ancillary && *Ancillary && !(*Ancillary)->AfdBarData_Data.empty())
2596 {
2597 Element_Trace_Begin1("Active Format Description & Bar Data");
2598
2599 //Parsing
2600 if (AfdBarData_Parser==NULL)
2601 {
2602 AfdBarData_Parser=new File_AfdBarData;
2603 Open_Buffer_Init(AfdBarData_Parser);
2604 ((File_AfdBarData*)AfdBarData_Parser)->Format=File_AfdBarData::Format_S2016_3;
2605 }
2606 if (AfdBarData_Parser->PTS_DTS_Needed)
2607 AfdBarData_Parser->FrameInfo.DTS=FrameInfo.DTS;
2608 if (!AfdBarData_Parser->Status[IsFinished])
2609 Open_Buffer_Continue(AfdBarData_Parser, (*Ancillary)->AfdBarData_Data[0]->Data, (*Ancillary)->AfdBarData_Data[0]->Size);
2610
2611 //Removing data from stack
2612 delete (*Ancillary)->AfdBarData_Data[0]; //(*Ancillary)->AfdBarData_Data[0]=NULL;
2613 (*Ancillary)->AfdBarData_Data.erase((*Ancillary)->AfdBarData_Data.begin());
2614
2615 Element_Trace_End0();
2616 }
2617 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
2618
2619 //Counting
2620 if (!MustExtendParsingDuration && File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Size==File_Size)
2621 Frame_Count_Valid=Frame_Count; //Finish frames in case of there are less than Frame_Count_Valid frames
2622 if (!TimeCodeIsNotTrustable && (picture_coding_type==1 || picture_coding_type==2)) //IFrame or PFrame
2623 {
2624 Time_End_Frames++; //One frame
2625 if (progressive_sequence && repeat_first_field)
2626 {
2627 Time_End_Frames++; //Frame repeated a second time
2628 if (top_field_first)
2629 Time_End_Frames++; //Frame repeated a third time
2630 }
2631 }
2632 Frame_Count++;
2633 Frame_Count_InThisBlock++;
2634 if (IFrame_IsParsed && Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1)
2635 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded++;
2636 if (!(progressive_sequence || picture_structure==3))
2637 {
2638 Field_Count++;
2639 Field_Count_InThisBlock++;
2640 }
2641 if (picture_coding_type==3)
2642 BVOP_Count++;
2643 else
2644 BVOPsSinceLastRefFrames=0;
2645 if (RefFramesCount<2 && (picture_coding_type==1 || picture_coding_type==2))
2646 RefFramesCount++;
2647 if (repeat_first_field)
2648 {
2649 if (progressive_sequence)
2650 {
2651 tc_ToAdd+=tc;
2652 if (top_field_first)
2653 tc_ToAdd+=tc;
2654 }
2655 else
2656 tc_ToAdd+=tc/2;
2657 }
2658 if (FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
2659 {
2660 FrameInfo.DTS+=tc_ToAdd;
2661 if (DTS_End<FrameInfo.DTS)
2662 DTS_End=FrameInfo.DTS;
2663 }
2664 if (FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1)
2665 {
2666 if (FrameInfo.PTS+tc_ToAdd>PTS_End || (PTS_End>1000000000 && FrameInfo.PTS+tc_ToAdd<=PTS_End-1000000000)) //More than current PTS_End or less than current PTS_End minus 1 second (there is a problem?)
2667 {
2668 PTS_End=FrameInfo.PTS+tc_ToAdd;
2669 PTS_End_temporal_reference=temporal_reference;
2670 }
2671 if (low_delay)
2672 FrameInfo.PTS+=tc_ToAdd;
2673 else
2674 FrameInfo.PTS=(int64u)-1; //With repeat_first_field option, it is impossible to know what is the next PTS
2675 }
2676
2677 //NextCode
2678 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
2679 {
2680 NextCode_Clear();
2681 NextCode_Add(0x00);
2682 NextCode_Add(0xB3);
2683 NextCode_Add(0xB8);
2684 }
2685
2686 //Autorisation of other streams
2687 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2688 if (!Macroblocks_Parse)
2689 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2690 for (int8u Pos=0x01; Pos<=0xAF; Pos++)
2691 Streams[Pos].Searching_Payload=false;
2692
2693 //Filling only if not already done
2694 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
2695 Accept("MPEG Video");
2696 if (!MustExtendParsingDuration && IFrame_Count==8)
2697 Frame_Count_Valid=Frame_Count; //We have enough frames
2698 if (!Status[IsFilled] && Frame_Count>=Frame_Count_Valid)
2699 {
2700 Fill("MPEG Video");
2701 if (File_Size==(int64u)-1)
2702 Finish("MPEG Video");
2703 else if (!IsSub && 2*(File_Offset+Buffer_Size+SizeToAnalyse_End)<File_Size && Config->ParseSpeed<1.0)
2704 {
2705 Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
2706 GoToFromEnd(SizeToAnalyse_End);
2707 }
2708 }
2709
2710 //Skipping slices (if already unpacketized)
2711 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2712 if (Demux_UnpacketizeContainer && Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset<Demux_TotalBytes
2713 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2714 && !Macroblocks_Parse
2715 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2716 )
2717 {
2718 Element_Offset=Demux_TotalBytes-(Buffer_TotalBytes+Buffer_Offset);
2719 }
2720 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2721
2722 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
2723 Ibi_SliceParsed=true;
2724 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
2725 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2726 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
2727 {
2728 macroblock_x++;
2729 Element_Info1(Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_x)+__T(" macroblocks"));
2730 macroblock_x_PerFrame+=macroblock_x;
2731 macroblock_y_PerFrame++;
2732 }
2733 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2734
2735 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2736 if (Slices_Count)
2737 return;
2738 Slices_Count++;
2739
2740 //sequence_header
2741 if (picture_coding_type==1 && (!Has_sequence_header || !Has_sequence_extension))
2742 {
2743 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
2744 if (!InitDataNotRepeated_Optional && !Has_sequence_header) //Currently we test only sequence_header
2745 {
2746 InitDataNotRepeated++;
2747
2748 //Testing if we must give up
2749 if (Config_InitDataNotRepeated_GiveUp && InitDataNotRepeated>=Config_InitDataNotRepeated_Occurences)
2750 Config->ParseSpeed=0; // Give up
2751 }
2752 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
2753 }
2754 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2755
2756 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2757 //Packets
2758 Has_sequence_header=false;
2759 Has_sequence_extension=false;
2760 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
2761 FILLING_END();
2762}
2763
2764//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2765// Packet Packet "01" --> "AF", slice_start, macroblock
2766#if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2767enum Mpegv_macroblock_type_config //bitwise
2768{
2769 spatial_temporal_weight_code_flag =0x01,
2770 macroblock_intra =0x02,
2771 macroblock_pattern =0x04,
2772 macroblock_motion_backward =0x08,
2773 macroblock_motion_forward =0x10,
2774 macroblock_quant =0x20,
2775};
2776void File_Mpegv::slice_start_macroblock()
2777{
2778 frame_motion_type=(int8u)-1;
2779 spatial_temporal_weight_code=0;
2780
2781 Element_Trace_Begin1("macroblock");
2782
2783 size_t macroblock_address_increment;
2784 do
2785 {
2786 Get_VL(macroblock_address_increment_Vlc, macroblock_address_increment, "macroblock_address_increment");
2787 Element_Info1(__T("macroblock_address_increment=")+Ztring::ToZtring(Mpegv_macroblock_address_increment[macroblock_address_increment].mapped_to3));
2788 if (macroblock_x!=(int64u)-1)
2789 macroblock_x+=Mpegv_macroblock_address_increment[macroblock_address_increment].mapped_to3;
2790 }
2791 while (Mpegv_macroblock_address_increment[macroblock_address_increment].mapped_to1==2); //Escape code
2792 if (macroblock_x==(int64u)-1)
2793 macroblock_x=0;
2794 Element_Info1(__T("macroblock_x=")+Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_x));
2795 Element_Trace_Begin1("macroblock_modes");
2796 vlc_fast* macroblock_type_X;
2797 switch(picture_coding_type)
2798 {
2799 case 1: macroblock_type_X=&macroblock_type_I; break;
2800 case 2: macroblock_type_X=&macroblock_type_P; break;
2801 case 3: macroblock_type_X=&macroblock_type_B; break;
2802 default : Element_DoNotTrust("Wrong picture_coding_type");
2803 Element_Trace_End0();
2804 Element_Trace_End0();
2805 return;
2806 }
2807 size_t macroblock_type_offset;
2808 Get_VL(*macroblock_type_X, macroblock_type_offset, "macroblock_type");
2809 macroblock_type=macroblock_type_X->Vlc[macroblock_type_offset].mapped_to3;
2810 if (!Synched)
2811 {
2812 BS_End();
2813 Element_Offset=Element_Size;
2814 return;
2815 }
2816 Element_Info1(__T("macroblock_quant=")+Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_type&macroblock_quant));
2817 Element_Info1(__T("macroblock_motion_forward=")+Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_type&macroblock_motion_forward));
2818 Element_Info1(__T("macroblock_motion_backward=")+Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_type&macroblock_motion_backward));
2819 Element_Info1(__T("macroblock_pattern=")+Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_type&macroblock_pattern));
2820 Element_Info1(__T("macroblock_intra=")+Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_type&macroblock_intra));
2821 Element_Info1(__T("spatial_temporal_weight_code_flag=")+Ztring::ToZtring(macroblock_type&spatial_temporal_weight_code_flag));
2822 if (macroblock_type&spatial_temporal_weight_code_flag
2823 && spatial_temporal_weight_code_table_index)
2824 Get_S1 (2, spatial_temporal_weight_code, "spatial_temporal_weight_code");
2825 if (macroblock_type&macroblock_intra
2826 && concealment_motion_vectors)
2827 frame_motion_type=2;
2828 if (macroblock_type&macroblock_motion_forward
2829 || macroblock_type&macroblock_motion_backward)
2830 {
2831 if (picture_structure==3) //Frame
2832 {
2833 if (!frame_pred_frame_dct)
2834 Get_S1(2, frame_motion_type, "frame_motion_type");
2835 else
2836 frame_motion_type=2;
2837 }
2838 else
2839 Get_S1 (2, field_motion_type, "field_motion_type");
2840 }
2841 if (picture_structure==3 //Frame
2842 && !frame_pred_frame_dct
2843 && (macroblock_type&macroblock_intra
2844 || macroblock_type&macroblock_pattern))
2845 Skip_SB( "dct_type");
2846 Element_Trace_End0();
2847 if (macroblock_type&macroblock_quant)
2848 Skip_S1(5, "quantiser_scale_code");
2849 if (macroblock_type&macroblock_motion_forward
2850 || (macroblock_type&macroblock_intra
2851 && concealment_motion_vectors))
2852 slice_start_macroblock_motion_vectors(false);
2853 if (macroblock_type&macroblock_motion_backward)
2854 slice_start_macroblock_motion_vectors(true);
2855 if (macroblock_type&macroblock_intra
2856 && concealment_motion_vectors)
2857 Mark_1();
2858 if (macroblock_type&macroblock_pattern)
2859 slice_start_macroblock_coded_block_pattern();
2860 for (int8u i=0; i<block_count; i++)
2861 slice_start_macroblock_block(i);
2862 Element_Trace_End0();
2863}
2864#endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
2865
2866//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2867// Packet Packet "01" --> "AF", slice_start, macroblock, motion_vectors

3079//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3080// Packet "B2"
3081void File_Mpegv::user_data_start()
3082{
3083 Element_Name("user_data_start");
3084
3085 //GA94 stuff
3086 if (Element_Size>=4)
3087 {
3088 int32u GA94_Identifier;
3089 Peek_B4(GA94_Identifier);
3090 switch (GA94_Identifier)
3091 {
3092 case 0x434301F8 : user_data_start_CC(); return;
3093 case 0x44544731 : user_data_start_DTG1(); return;
3094 case 0x47413934 : user_data_start_GA94(); return;
3095 default : {
3096 int8u SCTE20_Identifier;
3097 Peek_B1(SCTE20_Identifier);
3098 if (SCTE20_Identifier==0x03)
3099 {
3100 user_data_start_3();
3101 return;
3102 }
3103 }
3104 }
3105 }
3106
3107 //Rejecting junk at the begin
3108 size_t Library_Start_Offset=0;
3109 while (Library_Start_Offset+4<=Element_Size)
3110 {
3111 bool OK=true;
3112 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<4; Pos++)
3113 {
3114 if (!((Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]==0x20 && Pos)
3115 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]==0x22
3116 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]==0x27
3117 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]==0x28
3118 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]==0x29 && Pos)
3119 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]>=0x30
3120 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]<=0x3F)
3121 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]>=0x41
3122 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_Start_Offset+Pos]<=0x7D)))
3123 {
3124 OK=false;
3125 break;
3126 }
3127 }
3128 if (OK)
3129 break;
3130 Library_Start_Offset++;
3131 }
3132 if (Library_Start_Offset+4>Element_Size)
3133 {
3134 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "junk");
3135 return; //No good info
3136 }
3137
3138 //Accepting good data after junk
3139 size_t Library_End_Offset=Library_Start_Offset+4;
3140 while (Library_End_Offset<Element_Size
3141 && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_End_Offset]==0x0D
3142 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_End_Offset]==0x0A
3143 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_End_Offset]>=0x20 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_End_Offset]<=0x3F)
3144 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_End_Offset]>=0x41 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Library_End_Offset]<=0x7D)))
3145 Library_End_Offset++;
3146
3147 //Parsing
3148 Ztring Temp;
3149 if (Library_Start_Offset>0)
3150 Skip_XX(Library_Start_Offset, "junk");
3151 if (Library_End_Offset-Library_Start_Offset)
3152 Get_Local(Library_End_Offset-Library_Start_Offset, Temp,"data");
3153 if (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
3154 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "junk");
3155
3156 //Cleanup
3157 while(Temp.size()>3 && Temp[1]==__T('e') && Temp[2]==__T('n') && Temp[3]==__T('c'))
3158 Temp.erase(0, 1);
3159 while(Temp.size()>5 && Temp[3]==__T('M') && Temp[4]==__T('P') && Temp[5]==__T('E'))
3160 Temp.erase(0, 1);
3161
3162 //Cleanup
3163 while(!Temp.empty() && Temp[0]==__T('0'))
3164 Temp.erase(0, 1);
3165
3166 FILLING_BEGIN();
3167 if (!Temp.empty())
3168 {
3169 if (Temp.find(__T("build"))==0)
3170 Library+=Ztring(__T(" "))+Temp;
3171 else
3172 Library=Temp;
3173
3174 //Library
3175 if (Temp.find(__T("Created with Nero"))==0)
3176 {
3177 Library_Name=__T("Ahead Nero");
3178 }
3179 else if (Library.find(__T("encoded by avi2mpg1 ver "))==0)
3180 {
3181 Library_Name=__T("avi2mpg1");
3182 Library_Version=Library.SubString(__T("encoded by avi2mpg1 ver "), __T(""));
3183 }
3184 else if (Library.find(__T("encoded by TMPGEnc (ver. "))==0)
3185 {
3186 Library_Name=__T("TMPGEnc");
3187 Library_Version=Library.SubString(__T("encoded by TMPGEnc (ver. "), __T(")"));
3188 }
3189 else if (Library.find(__T("encoded by TMPGEnc 4.0 XPress Version. "))==0)
3190 {
3191 Library_Name=__T("TMPGEnc XPress");
3192 Library_Version=Library.SubString(__T("encoded by TMPGEnc 4.0 XPress Version. "), __T(""));
3193 }
3194 else if (Library.find(__T("encoded by TMPGEnc MPEG Editor "))==0)
3195 {
3196 Library_Name=__T("TMPGEnc MPEG Editor");
3197 Library_Version=Library.SubString(__T("Version. "), __T(""));
3198 }
3199 else if (Library.find(__T("encoded by TMPGEnc "))==0)
3200 {
3201 Library_Name=__T("TMPGEnc");
3202 Library_Version=Library.SubString(__T("encoded by TMPGEnc "), __T(""));
3203 }
3204 else if (Library.find(__T("MPEG Encoder v"))==0)
3205 {
3206 Library_Name=__T("MPEG Encoder by Tristan Savatier");
3207 Library_Version=Library.SubString(__T("MPEG Encoder v"), __T(" by"));
3208 }
3209 else
3210 Library_Name=Library;
3211
3212 }
3213 FILLING_END();
3214}

3368//---------------------------------------------------------------------------

3370void File_Mpegv::user_data_start_DTG1()
3371{

3378 if (DTG1_Parser==NULL)

3380 DTG1_Parser=new File_AfdBarData;
3381 Open_Buffer_Init(DTG1_Parser);
3382 ((File_AfdBarData*)DTG1_Parser)->Format=File_AfdBarData::Format_A53_4_DTG1;
3383
3384 //Aspect ratio for AFD
3385 float32 DAR=0;
3386 if (MPEG_Version==2)
3387 {
3388 if (aspect_ratio_information==0)
3389 ; //Forbidden
3390 else if (aspect_ratio_information==1)
3391 DAR=((float32)(0x1000*horizontal_size_extension+horizontal_size_value))/(0x1000*vertical_size_extension+vertical_size_value);
3392 else if (display_horizontal_size && display_vertical_size)
3393 {
3394 if (vertical_size_value && Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information])
3395 DAR=((float32)(0x1000*horizontal_size_extension+horizontal_size_value))/(0x1000*vertical_size_extension+vertical_size_value)

3397 }
3398 else if (Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information])
3399 DAR=Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information];
3400 }
3401 else //Version 1
3402 {
3403 if (vertical_size_value && Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information])
3404 DAR=((float32)(0x1000*horizontal_size_extension+horizontal_size_value))/(0x1000*vertical_size_extension+vertical_size_value)/Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information];
3405 }
3406 if (DAR>=1.330 && DAR<1.336) ((File_AfdBarData*)DTG1_Parser)->aspect_ratio_FromContainer=0; //4/3
3407 if (DAR>=1.774 && DAR<1.780) ((File_AfdBarData*)DTG1_Parser)->aspect_ratio_FromContainer=1; //16/9
3408 }
3409 if (DTG1_Parser->PTS_DTS_Needed)
3410 {
3411 DTG1_Parser->FrameInfo.PCR=FrameInfo.PCR;
3412 DTG1_Parser->FrameInfo.PTS=FrameInfo.PTS;
3413 DTG1_Parser->FrameInfo.DTS=FrameInfo.DTS;
3414 }
3415 Open_Buffer_Continue(DTG1_Parser, Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset, (size_t)(Element_Size-Element_Offset));
3416 Element_Offset=Element_Size;
3417 #else //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
3418 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Active Format Description");
3419 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_AFDBARDATA_YES)
3420}

3422//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3423// Packet "B2", GA94
3424void File_Mpegv::user_data_start_GA94()
3425{
3426 //Parsing
3427 int8u user_data_type_code;
3428 Skip_B4( "GA94_identifier");
3429 Get_B1 (user_data_type_code, "user_data_type_code");
3430 switch (user_data_type_code)
3431 {
3432 case 0x03 : user_data_start_GA94_03(); break;
3433 case 0x06 : user_data_start_GA94_06(); break;
3434 default : Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "GA94_reserved_user_data");
3435 }
3436}

3438//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3439// Packet "B2", GA94 0x03 (styled captioning)
3440void File_Mpegv::user_data_start_GA94_03()
3441{
3442 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
3443 GA94_03_IsPresent=true;
3444 MustExtendParsingDuration=true;
3445 Buffer_TotalBytes_Fill_Max=(int64u)-1; //Disabling this feature for this format, this is done in the parser
3446
3447 Element_Info1("DTVCC Transport");
3448
3449 //Coherency
3450 if (TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference>=TemporalReference.size())
3451 return;
3452
3453 //Purging too old orphelins
3454 if (GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset+8<TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference)
3455 {
3456 size_t Pos=TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference;
3457 do
3458 {
3459 if (TemporalReference[Pos]==NULL || !TemporalReference[Pos]->IsValid || TemporalReference[Pos]->GA94_03==NULL)
3460 break;
3461 Pos--;
3462 }
3463 while (Pos>0);
3464 GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset=Pos+1;
3465 }
3466
3467 if (TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference>=TemporalReference.size())
3468 TemporalReference.resize(TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference+1);
3469 temporalreference* &Ref=TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference];
3470 if (Ref==NULL)
3471 Ref=new temporalreference;
3472 if (Ref->GA94_03==NULL)
3473 Ref->GA94_03=new temporalreference::buffer_data;
3474 temporalreference::buffer_data* NewBuffer=Ref->GA94_03;
3475 int8u* NewData=new int8u[NewBuffer->Size+(size_t)(Element_Size-Element_Offset)];
3476 if (NewBuffer->Size)
3477 {
3478 //Data already present, copying in the new buffer
3479 std::memcpy(NewData, NewBuffer->Data, NewBuffer->Size);
3480 delete[] NewBuffer->Data; //Reassignement done below
3481 }
3482 NewBuffer->Data=NewData;
3483 std::memcpy(NewBuffer->Data+ NewBuffer->Size, Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset, (size_t)(Element_Size-Element_Offset));
3484 NewBuffer->Size+=(size_t)(Element_Size-Element_Offset);
3485
3486 //Parsing
3487 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "CC data");
3488
3489 //Parsing Captions after reordering
3490 bool CanBeParsed=true;
3491 for (size_t GA94_03_Pos=GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset; GA94_03_Pos<TemporalReference.size(); GA94_03_Pos++)
3492 if (TemporalReference[GA94_03_Pos]==NULL || !TemporalReference[GA94_03_Pos]->IsValid || TemporalReference[GA94_03_Pos]->GA94_03==NULL)
3493 CanBeParsed=false; //There is a missing field/frame
3494 if (CanBeParsed)
3495 {
3496 for (size_t GA94_03_Pos=GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset; GA94_03_Pos<TemporalReference.size(); GA94_03_Pos++)
3497 {
3498 Element_Begin1("Reordered DTVCC Transport");
3499
3500 //Parsing
3501 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3502 Element_Code=0x4741393400000003LL;
3503 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3504 if (GA94_03_Parser==NULL)
3505 {
3506 GA94_03_Parser=new File_DtvccTransport;
3507 Open_Buffer_Init(GA94_03_Parser);
3508 ((File_DtvccTransport*)GA94_03_Parser)->Format=File_DtvccTransport::Format_A53_4_GA94_03;
3509 }
3510 if (GA94_03_Parser->PTS_DTS_Needed)
3511 {
3512 GA94_03_Parser->FrameInfo.PCR=FrameInfo.PCR;
3513 GA94_03_Parser->FrameInfo.PTS=FrameInfo.PTS-(FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1?((TemporalReference.size()-1-GA94_03_Pos)*tc):0);
3514 GA94_03_Parser->FrameInfo.DTS=FrameInfo.DTS-(FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1?((TemporalReference.size()-1-GA94_03_Pos)*tc):0);
3515 }
3516 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3517 int8u Demux_Level_Save=Demux_Level;
3518 Demux_Level=8; //Ancillary
3519 Demux(TemporalReference[GA94_03_Pos]->GA94_03->Data, TemporalReference[GA94_03_Pos]->GA94_03->Size, ContentType_MainStream);
3520 Demux_Level=Demux_Level_Save;
3521 #endif // MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
3522 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_EIA608_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_EIA708_YES)
3523 GA94_03_Parser->ServiceDescriptors=ServiceDescriptors;
3524 #endif
3525 ((File_DtvccTransport*)GA94_03_Parser)->AspectRatio=MPEG_Version==1?Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information]:Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information];
3526 Open_Buffer_Continue(GA94_03_Parser, TemporalReference[GA94_03_Pos]->GA94_03->Data, TemporalReference[GA94_03_Pos]->GA94_03->Size);
3527
3528 Element_End0();
3529 }
3530 GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset=TemporalReference.size();
3531 }
3532 #else //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
3533 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "DTVCC Transport data");
3534 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
3535}

3565//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3566// Packet "B3"
3567void File_Mpegv::sequence_header()
3568{
3569 Element_Name("sequence_header");
3570
3571 //Reset
3572 display_horizontal_size=0;
3573 display_vertical_size=0;
3574
3575 //Reading
3576 int32u bit_rate_value_temp;
3577 BS_Begin();
3578 Get_S2 (12, horizontal_size_value, "horizontal_size_value");
3579 Get_S2 (12, vertical_size_value, "vertical_size_value");
3580 Get_S1 ( 4, aspect_ratio_information, "aspect_ratio_information"); Param_Info1C((vertical_size_value && Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information]), (float)horizontal_size_value/vertical_size_value/Mpegv_aspect_ratio1[aspect_ratio_information]); Param_Info1(Mpegv_aspect_ratio2[aspect_ratio_information]);
3581 Get_S1 ( 4, frame_rate_code, "frame_rate_code"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code]);
3582 Get_S3 (18, bit_rate_value_temp, "bit_rate_value"); Param_Info1(bit_rate_value_temp*400);
3583 Mark_1 ();
3584 Get_S2 (10, vbv_buffer_size_value, "vbv_buffer_size_value"); Param_Info2(2*1024*((int32u)vbv_buffer_size_value), " bytes");
3585 Skip_SB( "constrained_parameters_flag");
3586 TEST_SB_GET(load_intra_quantiser_matrix, "load_intra_quantiser_matrix");
3587 bool FillMatrix=Matrix_intra.empty();
3588 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<64; Pos++)
3589 {
3590 int8u intra_quantiser;
3591 Get_S1 (8, intra_quantiser, "intra_quantiser");
3592 if (FillMatrix)
3593 {
3594 Ztring Value=Ztring::ToZtring(intra_quantiser, 16);
3595 if (Value.size()==1)
3596 Value.insert(0, __T("0"));
3597 Matrix_intra+=Value;
3598 }
3599 }
3600 TEST_SB_END();
3601 TEST_SB_GET(load_non_intra_quantiser_matrix, "load_non_intra_quantiser_matrix");
3602 bool FillMatrix=Matrix_nonintra.empty();
3603 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<64; Pos++)
3604 {
3605 int8u non_intra_quantiser;
3606 Get_S1 (8, non_intra_quantiser, "non_intra_quantiser");
3607 if (FillMatrix)
3608 {
3609 Ztring Value=Ztring::ToZtring(non_intra_quantiser, 16);
3610 if (Value.size()==1)
3611 Value.insert(0, __T("0"));
3612 Matrix_nonintra+=Value;
3613 }
3614 }
3615 TEST_SB_END();
3616 BS_End();
3617
3618 //0x00 at the end
3619 if (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
3620 {
3621 int64u NullBytes_Begin=Element_Size-1;
3622 while (NullBytes_Begin>Element_Offset && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)NullBytes_Begin]==0x00)
3623 NullBytes_Begin--;
3624
3625 if (NullBytes_Begin==Element_Offset)
3626 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Padding");
3627 }
3628
3629 FILLING_BEGIN_PRECISE();
3630 temporal_reference_Adapt(); //TODO: this line should not exist but some streams do not have group_start and/or do not start from temporal_reference 0, fast and dirty patch
3631
3632 //Bit_rate
3633 if (bit_rate_value_IsValid && bit_rate_value_temp!=bit_rate_value)
3634 bit_rate_value_IsValid=false; //two bit_rate_values, not handled.
3635 else if (bit_rate_value==0)
3636 {
3637 bit_rate_value=bit_rate_value_temp;
3638 bit_rate_value_IsValid=true;
3639 }
3640
3641 //NextCode
3642 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
3643 {
3644 NextCode_Clear();
3645 NextCode_Add(0x00);
3646 NextCode_Add(0xB2);
3647 NextCode_Add(0xB5);
3648 NextCode_Add(0xB8);
3649 }
3650
3651 //Autorisation of other streams
3652 Streams[0x00].Searching_Payload=true;
3653 Streams[0xB2].Searching_Payload=true;
3654 Streams[0xB5].Searching_Payload=true;
3655 if (Frame_Count==0)
3656 Streams[0xB8].Searching_TimeStamp_Start=true;
3657 Streams[0xB8].Searching_TimeStamp_End=true;
3658
3659 //Temp
3660 if (Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code])
3661 tc=float64_int64s(((float64)1000000000)/Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code]);
3662 if (Frame_Count<Frame_Count_Valid)
3663 {
3664 FrameRate=Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code];
3665 SizeToAnalyse_Begin=((int64u)bit_rate_value)*50*2; //standard delay between TimeStamps is 0.7s, we try 2s to be sure to have at least 2 timestamps (for integrity checking)
3666 SizeToAnalyse_End=((int64u)bit_rate_value)*50*2; //standard delay between TimeStamps is 0.7s, we try 2s to be sure
3667 }
3668
3669 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3670 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
3671 block_count=6; //chroma_format default to 4:2:0
3672 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3673
3674 //Setting as OK
3675 sequence_header_IsParsed=true;
3676 if (Frame_Count==0 && FrameInfo.DTS==(int64u)-1)
3677 FrameInfo.DTS=0; //No DTS in container
3678
3679 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
3680 //
3681 Has_sequence_header=true;
3682 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
3683 FILLING_END();
3684}
