3693//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3694// Packet "B5"
3695void File_Mpegv::extension_start()
3696{
3697 Element_Name("extension_start");
3698 MPEG_Version=2; //extension_start only exists in MPEG-2 specs
3699
3700 //Parsing
3701 int8u extension_start_code_identifier;
3702 BS_Begin();
3703 Get_S1 ( 4, extension_start_code_identifier, "extension_start_code_identifier"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_extension_start_code_identifier[extension_start_code_identifier]);
3704 Element_Info1(Mpegv_extension_start_code_identifier[extension_start_code_identifier]);
3705
3706 switch (extension_start_code_identifier)
3707 {
3708 case 1 : //Sequence
3709 {
3710 //Parsing
3711 Peek_SB(profile_and_level_indication_escape);
3712 if (profile_and_level_indication_escape)
3713 {
3714 Get_S1 ( 8, profile_and_level_indication, "profile_and_level_indication"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication(profile_and_level_indication));
3715 }
3716 else
3717 {
3718 Skip_SB( "profile_and_level_indication_escape");
3719 Get_S1 ( 3, profile_and_level_indication_profile, "profile_and_level_indication_profile"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_profile[profile_and_level_indication_profile]);
3720 Get_S1 ( 4, profile_and_level_indication_level, "profile_and_level_indication_level"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_level[profile_and_level_indication_level]);
3721 }
3722 Get_SB ( progressive_sequence, "progressive_sequence");
3723 Get_S1 ( 2, chroma_format, "chroma_format"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_Colorimetry_format[chroma_format]);
3724 Get_S1 ( 2, horizontal_size_extension, "horizontal_size_extension");
3725 Get_S1 ( 2, vertical_size_extension, "vertical_size_extension");
3726 Get_S2 (12, bit_rate_extension, "bit_rate_extension");
3727 Mark_1 ();
3728 Get_S1 ( 8, vbv_buffer_size_extension, "vbv_buffer_size_extension"); Param_Info2(2*1024*((((int32u)vbv_buffer_size_extension)<<10)+vbv_buffer_size_value), " bytes");
3729 Get_SB ( low_delay, "low_delay");
3730 Get_S1 ( 2, frame_rate_extension_n, "frame_rate_extension_n");
3731 Get_S1 ( 5, frame_rate_extension_d, "frame_rate_extension_d");
3732 BS_End();
3733
3734 FILLING_BEGIN();
3735 if (frame_rate_extension_d)
3736 {
3737 FrameRate*=frame_rate_extension_n+1;
3738 FrameRate/=frame_rate_extension_d+1;
3739 }
3740 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3741 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
3742 block_count=Mpegv_block_count[chroma_format];
3743 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3744
3745 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
3746 //
3747 Has_sequence_extension=true;
3748 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED || MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
3749 FILLING_END();
3750 }
3751 break;
3752 case 2 : //Sequence Display
3753 {
3754 //Parsing
3755 Get_S1 ( 3, video_format, "video_format"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_video_format[video_format]);
3756 TEST_SB_GET ( colour_description, "colour_description");
3757 Get_S1 (8, colour_primaries, "colour_primaries"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_colour_primaries(colour_primaries));
3758 Get_S1 (8, transfer_characteristics, "transfer_characteristics"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_transfer_characteristics(transfer_characteristics));
3759 Get_S1 (8, matrix_coefficients, "matrix_coefficients"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_matrix_coefficients(matrix_coefficients));
3760 TEST_SB_END();
3761 Get_S2 (14, display_horizontal_size, "display_horizontal_size");
3762 Mark_1 ();
3763 Get_S2 (14, display_vertical_size, "display_vertical_size");
3764 BS_End();
3765 }
3766 break;
3767 case 5 : //Sequence Scalable Extension
3768 {
3769 //Parsing
3770 Skip_S2(10, "lower_layer_temporal_reference");
3771 Mark_1();
3772 Skip_S2(15, "lower_layer_horizontal_offset");
3773 Mark_1();
3774 Skip_S2(15, "lower_layer_vertical_offset");
3775 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3776 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
3777 {
3778 sequence_scalable_extension_Present=true;
3779 Get_S1 ( 2, spatial_temporal_weight_code_table_index, "spatial_temporal_weight_code_table_index");
3780 }
3781 else
3782 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3783 Skip_S1( 2, "spatial_temporal_weight_code_table_index");
3784 Skip_SB( "lower_layer_progressive_frame");
3785 Skip_SB( "lower_layer_deinterlaced_field_select");
3786 BS_End();
3787 }
3788 break;
3789 case 8 : //Picture Coding
3790 {
3791 //Parsing
3792 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3793 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
3794 {
3795 Get_S1 ( 4, f_code[0][0], "f_code_forward_horizontal");
3796 Get_S1 ( 4, f_code[0][1], "f_code_forward_vertical");
3797 Get_S1 ( 4, f_code[1][0], "f_code_backward_horizontal");
3798 Get_S1 ( 4, f_code[1][1], "f_code_backward_vertical");
3799 }
3800 else
3801 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3802 {
3803 Skip_S1( 4, "f_code_forward_horizontal");
3804 Skip_S1( 4, "f_code_forward_vertical");
3805 Skip_S1( 4, "f_code_backward_horizontal");
3806 Skip_S1( 4, "f_code_backward_vertical");
3807 }
3808 Get_S1 ( 2, intra_dc_precision, "intra_dc_precision");
3809 Get_S1 ( 2, picture_structure, "picture_structure"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_picture_structure[picture_structure]);
3810 Get_SB ( top_field_first, "top_field_first");
3811 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3812 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
3813 {
3814 Get_SB ( frame_pred_frame_dct, "frame_pred_frame_dct");
3815 Get_SB ( concealment_motion_vectors, "concealment_motion_vectors");
3816 }
3817 else
3818 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3819 {
3820 Skip_SB( "frame_pred_frame_dct");
3821 Skip_SB( "concealment_motion_vectors");
3822 }
3823 Skip_SB( "q_scale_type");
3824 #if MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3825 if (Macroblocks_Parse)
3826 {
3827 Get_SB ( intra_vlc_format, "intra_vlc_format");
3828 }
3829 else
3830 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MACROBLOCKS
3831 {
3832 Skip_SB( "intra_vlc_format");
3833 }
3834 Skip_SB( "alternate_scan");
3835 Get_SB ( repeat_first_field, "repeat_first_field");
3836 Skip_SB( "chroma_420_type");
3837 Get_SB ( progressive_frame, "progressive_frame");
3838 TEST_SB_SKIP( "composite_display_flag");
3839 Skip_SB( "v_axis");
3840 Skip_S1( 3, "field_sequence");
3841 Skip_SB( "sub_carrier");
3842 Skip_S1( 7, "burst_amplitude");
3843 Skip_S1( 8, "sub_carrier_phase");
3844 TEST_SB_END();
3845 BS_End();
3846 }
3847
3848 FILLING_BEGIN();
3849 if (progressive_frame==false)
3850 {
3851 if (picture_structure==3) //Frame
3852 {
3853 if (top_field_first)
3854 Interlaced_Top++;
3855 else
3856 Interlaced_Bottom++;
3857 PictureStructure_Frame++;
3858 FirstFieldFound=false;
3859 if (TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference>=TemporalReference.size())
3860 TemporalReference.resize(TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference+1);
3861 if (TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]==NULL)
3862 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]=new temporalreference;
3863 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->picture_coding_type=picture_coding_type;
3864 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->progressive_frame=progressive_frame;
3865 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->picture_structure=picture_structure;
3866 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->top_field_first=top_field_first;
3867 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->repeat_first_field=repeat_first_field;
3868 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->HasPictureCoding=true;
3869 }
3870 else //Field
3871 {
3872 if (!FirstFieldFound)
3873 {
3874 if (picture_structure==1) //-Top
3875 Interlaced_Top++;
3876 else //-Bottom
3877 Interlaced_Bottom++;
3878 }
3879 FirstFieldFound=!FirstFieldFound;
3880 PictureStructure_Field++;
3881 }
3882 }
3883 else
3884 {
3885 progressive_frame_Count++;
3886 if (top_field_first)
3887 Interlaced_Top++;
3888 else
3889 Interlaced_Bottom++;
3890 PictureStructure_Frame++;
3891 if (picture_structure==3) //Frame
3892 {
3893 if (TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference>=TemporalReference.size())
3894 TemporalReference.resize(TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference+1);
3895 if (TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]==NULL)
3896 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]=new temporalreference;
3897 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->picture_coding_type=picture_coding_type;
3898 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->progressive_frame=progressive_frame;
3899 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->picture_structure=picture_structure;
3900 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->top_field_first=top_field_first;
3901 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->repeat_first_field=repeat_first_field;
3902 TemporalReference[TemporalReference_Offset+temporal_reference]->HasPictureCoding=true;
3903 }
3904 }
3905 FILLING_END();
3906 break;
3907 case 9 : //Picture Spatial Scalable Extension
3908 {
3909 //Parsing
3910 Skip_S1(4, "data");
3911 BS_End();
3912 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "data");
3913 }
3914 break;
3915 case 10 : //Picture Temporal Scalable Extension
3916 {
3917 //Parsing
3918 Skip_S1(4, "data");
3919 BS_End();
3920 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "data");
3921 }
3922 break;
3923 default :
3924 {
3925 //Parsing
3926 Skip_S1(4, "data");
3927 BS_End();
3928 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "data");
3929 }
3930 }
3931}

3933//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3934// Packet "B7"
3935void File_Mpegv::sequence_end()
3936{
3937 Element_Name("sequence_end");
3938
3939 if (!Status[IsFilled] && sequence_header_IsParsed)
3940 {
3941 //End of file, and we have some frames
3942 Accept("MPEG Video");
3943 Finish("MPEG Video");
3944 }
3945}

3947//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3948// Packet "B8"
3949void File_Mpegv::group_start()
3950{
3951 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
3952 {
3953 if (!NextCode_Test())
3954 return;
3955 }
3956 Element_Name("group_start");
3957
3958 //Reading
3959 int8u Hours, Minutes, Seconds, Frames;
3960 bool drop_frame_flag, closed_gop, broken_link;
3961 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
3962 if (Trace_Activated)
3963 {
3964 //Parsing
3965 BS_Begin();
3966 Get_SB ( drop_frame_flag, "time_code_drop_frame_flag");
3967 Get_S1 ( 5, Hours, "time_code_time_code_hours");
3968 Get_S1 ( 6, Minutes, "time_code_time_code_minutes");
3969 Mark_1();
3970 Get_S1 ( 6, Seconds, "time_code_time_code_seconds");
3971 Get_S1 ( 6, Frames, "time_code_time_code_pictures");
3972 Get_SB ( closed_gop, "closed_gop");
3973 Get_SB ( broken_link, "broken_link");
3974 BS_End();
3975 Ztring Time;
3976 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Hours);
3977 Time+=__T(':');
3978 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Minutes);
3979 Time+=__T(':');
3980 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Seconds);
3981 if (FrameRate!=0)
3982 {
3983 Time+=__T('.');
3984 Time+=Ztring::ToZtring(Frames*1000/FrameRate, 0);
3985 }
3986 Element_Info1(Time);
3987 }
3988 else
3989 {
3990 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
3991 //Parsing
3992 size_t Buffer_Pos=Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset;
3993 drop_frame_flag = (Buffer[Buffer_Pos ]&0x80)?true:false;
3994 Hours =((Buffer[Buffer_Pos ]&0x7C)>> 2);
3995 Minutes =((Buffer[Buffer_Pos ]&0x03)<< 4)
3996 | ((Buffer[Buffer_Pos+1] )>> 4);
3997 Seconds =((Buffer[Buffer_Pos+1]&0x07)<< 3)
3998 | ((Buffer[Buffer_Pos+2] )>> 5);
3999 Frames =((Buffer[Buffer_Pos+2]&0x1F)<< 1)
4000 | ((Buffer[Buffer_Pos+3] )>> 7);
4001 closed_gop = (Buffer[Buffer_Pos+3]&0x40)?true:false;
4002 broken_link = (Buffer[Buffer_Pos+3]&0x20)?true:false;
4003 Element_Offset+=4;
4004 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
4005 }
4006 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
4007
4008 FILLING_BEGIN();
4009 temporal_reference_Adapt();
4010
4011 //NextCode
4012 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
4013 {
4014 NextCode_Clear();
4015 NextCode_Add(0x00);
4016 NextCode_Add(0xB2);
4017 NextCode_Add(0xB5);
4018 NextCode_Add(0xB8);
4019 }
4020
4021 if (TimeCodeIsNotTrustable)
4022 return;
4023
4024 if (Time_Current_Seconds==0 && Time_Current_Frames==0 && Hours==0 && Minutes==0 && Seconds==0 && Frames==0)
4025 {
4026 //Time code is always 0
4027 TimeCodeIsNotTrustable=true;
4028 Time_End_Seconds=(size_t)-1;
4029 TimeCode_FirstFrame.clear();
4030 return;
4031 }
4032
4033 //Calculating
4034 Time_Current_Seconds=60*60*Hours+60*Minutes+Seconds;
4035 Time_Current_Frames =Frames;
4036
4037 if (!group_start_IsParsed)
4038 group_start_IsParsed=true;
4039 if (!group_start_FirstPass)
4040 {
4041 group_start_FirstPass=true;
4042 group_start_drop_frame_flag=drop_frame_flag;
4043 group_start_closed_gop=closed_gop;
4044 group_start_broken_link=broken_link;
4045
4046 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Hours/10);
4047 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Hours%10);
4048 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=':';
4049 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Minutes/10);
4050 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Minutes%10);
4051 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=':';
4052 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Seconds/10);
4053 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Seconds%10);
4054 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=drop_frame_flag?';':':';
4055 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Frames/10);
4056 TimeCode_FirstFrame+=('0'+Frames%10);
4057
4058 group_start_closed_gop_Closed=0;
4059 group_start_closed_gop_Open=0;
4060 }
4061
4062 if (closed_gop)
4063 group_start_closed_gop_Closed++;
4064 else
4065 group_start_closed_gop_Open++;
4066
4067 RefFramesCount=0;
4068
4069 //Autorisation of other streams
4070 if (Searching_TimeStamp_Start_DoneOneTime)
4071 Streams[0xB8].Searching_TimeStamp_Start=false; //group_start
4072 else
4073 Searching_TimeStamp_Start_DoneOneTime=true;
4074 Streams[0x00].Searching_TimeStamp_End=true; //picture_start
4075 FILLING_END();
4076}

4082//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4083// Packet "B8"
4084void File_Mpegv::temporal_reference_Adapt()
4085{
4086 //Temporal reference
4087 temporal_reference_Old=(int16u)-1;
4088 temporal_reference_Max=0;
4089 TemporalReference_Offset=TemporalReference.size();
4090 if (TemporalReference_Offset>=0x800)
4091 {
4092 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<0x400; Pos++)
4093 delete TemporalReference[Pos]; //TemporalReference[Pos]=NULL;
4094 TemporalReference.erase(TemporalReference.begin(), TemporalReference.begin()+0x400);
4095 if (0x400<TemporalReference_Offset)
4096 TemporalReference_Offset-=0x400;
4097 else
4098 TemporalReference_Offset=0;
4099 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
4100 if (0x400<GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset)
4101 GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset-=0x400;
4102 else
4103 GA94_03_TemporalReference_Offset=0;
4104 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
4105 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES)
4106 if (0x400<Scte_TemporalReference_Offset)
4107 Scte_TemporalReference_Offset-=0x400;
4108 else
4109 Scte_TemporalReference_Offset=0;
4110 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_SCTE20_YES)
4111 }
4112}

4114} //NameSpace
